targets.query: SELECT "current_ep"+1 FROM "dynamic_info" WHERE ("experiment" =~ /^$experiment$/ AND "is_train" = true) AND $timeFilter
SELECT "current_ep"+1 FROM "dynamic_info" WHERE ("experiment" =~ /^$experiment$/ AND "is_train" = false) AND $timeFilter
SELECT * FROM "vessel_usage" WHERE ("experiment" =~ /^$experiment$/ AND  "ep" = $episode and "vessel" = '$vessel' ) AND $timeFilter
SELECT /.policy$/, "action" FROM "q_value" WHERE ("experiment" = '$experiment' AND  "ep" = $episode AND "tick" = $action_tick) AND $timeFilter
